QuestData.Title: Blind the Eyes
QuestData.Description:
Strange forces have been interfering with my visions of late. The ever-watching eyes pierce through the veil, shattering my clairvoyance.
The eyes of our enemy peer into our very souls and pierce our minds. We must rip them out, if we truly wish to be rid of the curse on this land.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill $1oa Foul Observers in the Akhenet Fields in Uldum.
